text: Natalia Danielle Dyer (born January 13, 1995) is an American actress. She is best known for her starring role of Nancy Wheeler in the Netflix series Stranger Things. She started her career in 2009, appearing in Hannah Montana: The Movie as Clarissa Granger. Dyer was born in Nashville, Tennessee. She is a student at New York University. In addition to her acting career, Dyer's physical characteristics have been a subject of interest. She stands at a height of 5 feet 4 inches (162.56 cm) and weighs approximately 49 kg. Her body measurements are 34-25-36 inches (86-63.5-91.5 cm).
